item.title: Changes
item.description: Some pictures I’ve taken along many years (mostly while I have been at university since 2011), years full of changes, going from thinking and doing kinda stupid stuff, to thinking and doing either kinda more rational stuff or stupider stuff heh, a whole life learning, but also, just out of pure curiosity, trying several combinations of hair styles, sometimes even cutting my own hair myself to try things. (Or sometimes experimenting odd stuff just for one day).
